description: Manage a SQL Instance's encryption protector.

commands.name: az sql mi tde-key set
commands.summary: Sets the SQL Instance's encryption protector.
commands.syntax:
az sql mi tde-key set --server-key-type {AzureKeyVault, ServiceManaged}
                      [--auto-rotation-enabled {false, true}]
                      [--ids]
                      [--kid]
                      [--managed-instance]
                      [--resource-group]
                      [--subscription]
